<div class="row margin-bottom-10">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p>The rainforest is one of the places I absolutely must see during my Australian journey. Near Cairns, there's the Daintree National Park. I hope to find some good group day trips into the rainforest. I want to experience and photograph nature in its purest form. From Cairns, I'll head south along the Great Barrier Reef. My plan is to explore the reef both above and below the water.</p>
    </div>
</div>

