        <p>All told, I'll be covering over 12,000km in two different camper vans, plus more than 1,000km by bus. I'll have explored both main islands of New Zealand and all five regions of mainland Australia. I'll have taken at least four flights, hopefully including one on an Airbus A380. It's shaping up to be quite an adventure. I can hardly wait!</p>
